\par }{\b\ul\cf1\insrsid10765703\charrsid10765703 Luke 6:46-7:1}{\cf1\insrsid10765703  }{\cf1\insrsid10765703 And why call ye me, Lord, Lord, and do not the things which I say? 47 Whosoever cometh to me, and heareth my sayings, and doeth 
